Countable, NextValue<Minimum>, Sized, MapFactory<Long,Minimum>, Arithmetic<Minimum>, Castable, CastTrait, DoubleQuantizable, IntegerNumeric<Minimum>, Maximizable<Minimum>, Minimizable<Minimum>, Quantizable, QuantumComparable<Minimum>, Stringable, StringSource, Source<Long>, Comparable<Countable>, Supplier<Long>
public class Minimum extends BaseCount<Minimum>
A count value that is a minimum. This class mainly exists to clarify APIs by giving a meaning to the count value.
